00:07:19.280 --> 00:07:20.200
Qianfei.

00:07:20.960 --> 00:07:22.160
Felicidades.

00:07:22.240 --> 00:07:23.520
-Beberse todo. -Sí.

00:07:24.120 --> 00:07:26.320
